OL,3,CStaffing levels remain 'safety
OL,4,Cconcern' at hospital's maternity unit
OL,6,FSafe staffing levels in parts of a
OL,7,FSwansea hospital's midwifery unit
OL,8,F"remain a concern" according to
OL,9,Fhealthcare inspectors.
OL,11,FSingleton Hospital has faced continued
OL,12,Fcriticism over the last two years over
OL,13,Fthe safety of its maternity ward and
OL,14,Fthe latest Healthcare Inspectorate
OL,15,FWales (HIW) report found that there
OL,16,Fare still problems with the number of
OL,17,Fstaff on the Antenatal Assessment Unit.
