OL,6,FOverall, inspectors found significant
OL,7,Fimprovements to the service since its
OL,8,Flast inspection but it has sought
OL,9,Fimmediate assurance over staffing
OL,10,Flevels at the Antenatal Assessment
OL,11,FUnit.
OL,13,FInspectors said that further
OL,14,Fimprovement is still needed to ensure
OL,15,Fpeople are able to "consistently
OL,16,Freceive an acceptable standard of care
OL,17,Fwhen giving birth".
