OL,6,FAn ITV Wales This Week documentary in
OL,7,FOctober last year then revealed fresh
OL,8,Fallegations of poor care and a service
OL,9,Fthat continued to be impacted by
OL,10,Fcritical staffing levels.
OL,12,FThe Healthcare Inspectorate Wales
OL,13,Freport, which described it as
OL,14,F'unsafe', eventually led to the then
OL,15,FHealth Minister, Eluned Morgan MS,
OL,16,Fplacing it under enhanced monitoring.
