OL,6,FRobert Channon whose son Gethin was
OL,7,Fborn with severe brain damage after
OL,8,Fcomplications with his birth at
OL,9,FSingleton Hospital in 2019 has given
OL,10,Fhis reaction to the latest report.
OL,12,FHe said: "We welcome the latest HIW
OL,13,Freport with relief that after five
OL,14,Flong years since Gethin suffered an
OL,15,Fhorrific avoidable injury at birth
OL,16,Fthat improvements are starting to be
OL,17,Fmade.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
