OL,4,Cconcern' at hospital's maternity unit
OL,6,F"However when you dig into the detail
OL,7,Fthere are still clear and critical
OL,8,Fsafety issues. For example midwifery
OL,9,Fstaff told HIW that they don't have
OL,10,Faccess to essential medical equipment.
OL,11,FEmergency trollies missing and
OL,12,Fworryingly there are still staff
OL,13,Fshortages in certain units.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
