OL,3,CStaffing levels remain 'safety
OL,4,Cconcern' at hospital's maternity unit
OL,6,F"Several families have come forward to
OL,7,Fus recently around concerns with the
OL,8,Fantenatal assessment unit, something
OL,9,FHIW identified as an immediate
OL,10,Fassurance issue. Also it is upsetting
OL,11,Fto hear patients are still not given
OL,12,Fquick enough access to pain relief,
OL,13,Fsomething HIW found in September 2023.
OL,15,F"Overall the improvements made so far
OL,16,Fdo not assure us that the maternity
OL,17,Fservice in Swansea Bay is safe. It is
OL,18,Fnow even more important that the
OL,19,Findependent review is revamped to be
OL,20,Ffully independent and setup correctly,
OL,21,Fsomething which is still not in place."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
