OL,6,FLast month the woman conducting a
OL,7,Freview into maternity and neonatal
OL,8,Fservices at the health board stood
OL,9,Fdown with immediate effect.
OL,11,FIn the latest report inspectors found
OL,12,Fthat there were also concerns for
OL,13,Fpatient safety regarding the increase
OL,14,Fuse of agency staff and a lack of
OL,15,F"appropriate skill mix within the
OL,16,Funit".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
