OL,6,FAdditionally midwifery staff told
OL,7,Finspectors that they did not always
OL,8,Fhave access to essential medical
OL,9,Fequipment to provide sufficient care
OL,10,Fto patients.
OL,12,FHIW said it was also concerned to
OL,13,F"hear further feedback from women in
OL,14,Frelation to delays administering pain
OL,15,Fmedication, which was also reported
OL,16,Fduring our previous inspection".
OL,18,FIt has said that Swansea University
OL,19,FHealth Board must monitor, review and
OL,20,Fact upon feedback to avoid such delays.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
