OL,3,CStaffing levels remain 'safety
OL,4,Cconcern' at hospital's maternity unit
OL,6,FHowever inspectors did praise staff
OL,7,Ffor working hard, describing them as
OL,8,Fproviding "women and birthing people,
OL,9,Fand their families, with a positive
OL,10,Fexperience despite the sustained
OL,11,Fpressures on the unit".
OL,13,FThe Chief Executive of the HIW, Alun
OL,14,FJones, has said their inspection at
OL,15,Fthe hospital has highlighted the
OL,16,Fsustained challenges of maternity
OL,17,Fservices at the health board.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
