OL,3,CStaffing levels remain 'safety
OL,4,Cconcern' at hospital's maternity unit
OL,6,F"Whilst improvements were identified
OL,7,Fduring our return inspection, further
OL,8,Faction is required. I hope this report
OL,9,Fwill accelerate the measures taken to
OL,10,Fdrive forward timely improvements not
OL,11,Fonly patients, but for staff within
OL,12,Fthe maternity unit.
OL,14,F"We will be working with the health
OL,15,Fboard to ensure robust improvements
OL,16,Fare made and evidenced."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
