OL,6,FIn response to the report from
OL,7,Finspectors, Swansea Bay University
OL,8,FHealth Board have said: "We are fully
OL,9,Fcommitted to continuously improving
OL,10,Four maternity and neonatal services,
OL,11,Fand this latest HIW report recognises
OL,12,Fthe "significant improvements" already
OL,13,Fmade, particularly around staffing and
OL,14,Fservice leadership.
OL,16,F"However we acknowledge there is still
OL,17,Fmore to be done, and are taking firm
OL,18,Faction to complete all the outstanding
OL,19,Frecommendations.
