OL,6,F"The full report gives extensive
OL,7,Fdetails of the improvements made, as
OL,8,Fwell as our action plan, and we
OL,9,Fencourage all interested parties to
OL,10,Fread it through.
OL,12,F"The HIW report published today
OL,13,Ffollows a recent release of the most
OL,14,Fup-to-date UK-wide MBRRACE data. This
OL,15,Fdata, which is open to the public,
OL,16,Fdemonstrates that our maternity and
OL,17,Fneonatal mortality rate is lower than
OL,18,Fsimilar maternity and neonatal
OL,19,Fservices elsewhere in the UK."
